      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 16.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、mihoさんこそお疲れ様でした\nうまくいって安心しましたよ",
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます\n私達が、本番でミスなんてする訳ないでしょう",
      "startTime": 26.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……それで、{user}さん\n私、貴方に言わないといけないことがあって……",
      "startTime": 33.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……この後、少しお時間をいただけませんか？",
      "startTime": 36.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんが俺に話したいこと……？）\n（重要なことかよほど言い辛いか……なんだろう……？）",
      "startTime": 42.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "その、今回……",
      "startTime": 47.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっとすみません！　はい、お疲れ様です\nえ？　レコード会社の社長がいらっしゃってる？",
      "startTime": 54.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-vibe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 49.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2166.666666600001,
          "startTime": 51.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんすみません、急ぎみたいなんで\n行ってきます、でも話はちゃんと後で聞きますから！！",
      "startTime": 59.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5500,
          "startTime": 63.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "え……ええ",
      "startTime": 63.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その夜、旅館にて",
      "startTime": 67.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\nこんな遅くまで大変ですね",
      "startTime": 71.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、これが俺の仕事ですから\nそれで……mihoさん、俺に話というのは……",
      "startTime": 76.7083334075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "startTime": 81.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、今回は本当にすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 82.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "大事なツアーの最中に、旅館で大騒ぎして\nあまつさえ、記憶がなくなるまでお酒を飲むなんて",
      "startTime": 90.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、俺への話ってそのことですか？",
      "startTime": 94.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ\nこういうことは、ちゃんとけじめをつけないと",
      "startTime": 100.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、どんな難しい話なのかと思ってたんで……\nこのくらいなら、ツアーが終わった後でも良かったのに",
      "startTime": 107.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳にはいかないでしょう\n一応、貴方が私達のマネージャーなんですから",
      "startTime": 112.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "私達はまだ、星見プロに移って間もないですし\n今は人気を回復させる大事な時期なのに",
      "startTime": 120.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "ステージの出来で批判されるならともかく\nそれ以外の所で炎上なんてしたら、泣くに泣けません",
      "startTime": 127.0804708651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……私ってば、もうろくしてしまったのかしら",
      "startTime": 131.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（これはだいぶ落ち込んでるな……）\n（でも、慰めるよりmihoさんには……）",
      "startTime": 139.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは常に注目される仕事ですから……\nある意味、休みなどないと思っていただかないと",
      "startTime": 145.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ",
      "startTime": 148.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "特に、mihoさんは最年長な訳ですから\nステージの外でも、模範になっていただきたいですね",
      "startTime": 153.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "……はい\n……今後はこんなことがないように、気をつけます",
      "startTime": 158.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
